title: The Allman Brothers at Great Woods 1991
description:
This is the Allman Brothers from Great Woods in 1991 -- great concert. However, this is the botched DVD version that runs short and is missing Jessica while Blue Sky is overdubbed with interviews and Elizabeth Reed is edited. What can I say .. they made a mess. If you can find the VHS version .. get it! Still, sound and picture is great. This video is 55minutes total (VHS is roughly 90 min).

If I could find the VHS version in my vault and knew how to rip it I would .. one day maybe ;-)

Enjoy!
